title: GESES
description:
Join us for a high-energy night of Techno and Hard Bounce music!

**Headliner:**

**► GESES**


[Linktr.ee/iamgeses](http://linktr.ee/iamgeses)


GESES is the perfect balance between old-school techno trance and modern festival energy. His unique sound, known as Nu World Rave, is bringing a fresh vibe to both the American and global dance scenes. Over the last two years, GESES has built an impressive fanbase, becoming one of SoundCloud’s hottest remixers. His remixes and originals have gone viral, gaining international attention and leading to major collaborations with artists like Nicky Romero, Timmy Trumpet, Hardwell, Ben Nicky, 4B, Sigala & More.
